    "ingredients_text_with_allergens_ar": "PALEO BARSⓇ PECAN DATE NUTRITION INFORMATION Servings per package: 5 Serving size: 35 g (1 Bar) Avg. Quantity % Daily Intake* Avg. Quantity per Serving per Serving per 100 g Energy 704 kJ (168 Cal) 8% 2010 kJ (481 Cal) Protein 3.4 g 7% 9.7 g Fat, total 10.6 g 15% 30.4 g - saturated 1.0 g 4% 2.9 g Carbohydrate 13.3 g 4% 38.0 g sugars 13.1 g 15% 37.3g Dietary fibre Sodium 3.3g 11% 9.5g 12 mg 0.5% 33 mg *Percentage Daily Intakes are based on an average adult diet of 8700 kJ. Your daily intakes may be higher or lower depending on your energy needs. No Artificial Colours No Artificial Flavours No Preservatives Source of Dietary Fibre Ingredients: Dried Dates (52%), Crushed Pecan (28%), Almond Pieces (20%). CONTAINS ALMOND, <span class=\"allergen\">PECAN</span>. MAY CONTAIN WHEAT, <span class=\"allergen\">GLUTEN</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">BRAZIL NUT</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">CASHEW</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">HAZELNUT</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">MACADAMIA</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">WALNUT</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">MILK</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">PEANUT</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">SESAME</span>, <span class=\"allergen\">SOY</span>. Although every effort has been made to remove stones and shell, some small fragments may remain. Suitable for Vegetarians and Vegans. Store in a cool, dry place. Packed in Germany from imported ingredients MADE REAL® is a registered trademark of ALDI Stores. ALDI guarantees that our exclusive brand products are developed to our stringent quality specifications. If you are not entirely satisfied with this product, please return it to your nearest ALDI store for a full refund or replacement. ALDI STORES 1 SARGENTS ROAD MINCHINBURY NSW 2770 www.aldi.com.au Box Film B Get the latest recycling advice at arl.org.au Flatten to recycle Check locally",
